
1.Just jokingly talking about hacking into school networks can be taken seriously and can get the students 
in a lot of trouble

2.Hacking into the school's network is illegal because you can do lots of things if you get hold of that power
and can cause problems even if the students are just joking because these are matters that are not taken lightly

3.Hacking into school networks can give you access to a range of actions that can be used to change school 
policies to change your grades to all A's which is all very bad to do
